OL,3,CSharp rise in number of floods and
OL,4,Cfires recorded at NHS sites in the
OL,5,Cpast year
OL,7,FThe NHS has been hit by a rise in the
OL,8,Fnumber of floods and fires at its
OL,9,Fsites in the past year, analysis of
OL,10,Fofficial figures shows.
OL,12,FThe number of floods in 2022/23 was up
OL,13,Fby almost 60% on the previous 12
OL,14,Fmonths, with 279 incidents recorded.
OL,16,FThe incidents refer to flooding at NHS
OL,17,Fsites where water has caused
OL,18,Fdisruption, for example by breaching a
OL,19,Fbuilding or flooding an approach road.
